519
00:48:00,208 --> 00:48:04,379
Hyeon Min is apparently bringing some girl.

520
00:48:06,006 --> 00:48:07,840
Does that bother you?

521
00:48:09,426 --> 00:48:11,394
Can't you come with me?

522
00:48:12,187 --> 00:48:16,349
- I'd usually do you any favor, but—
- All right.

523
00:48:17,117 --> 00:48:18,743
Sorry for asking.

524
00:48:20,478 --> 00:48:22,856
Why did you ask me for a favor that you knew I couldn't do for you?

525
00:48:24,608 --> 00:48:27,284
That's not very good manners.

526
00:48:35,243 --> 00:48:39,805
All right. All I need is one million won.

527
00:48:55,113 --> 00:48:59,017
- Your offer is still valid, right?
- Of course.

528
00:49:00,076 --> 00:49:05,681
Fine. But in exchange, give me cash.
And I can't give you a tax receipt.

529
00:49:06,499 --> 00:49:09,944
You're quite amusing. That isn't what I expected you to say.

530
00:49:09,944 --> 00:49:14,223
Fine, then. But let me have a one plus one.

531
00:49:14,223 --> 00:49:16,000
What are you talking about?

532
00:49:16,000 --> 00:49:19,946
- Act like my fiancee for three hours.
- What? Your fiancee?

533
00:49:19,946 --> 00:49:21,539
What, you don't want to?

534
00:49:21,539 --> 00:49:23,466
You're never going to get another chance

535
00:49:23,466 --> 00:49:26,044
to earn so much money in three hours.

536
00:49:27,145 --> 00:49:29,730
Why do you need a fiancee for three hours?

537
00:49:31,174 --> 00:49:36,537
Oh, because of my grandfather.

538
00:49:36,537 --> 00:49:37,681
Your grandfather?

539
00:49:37,681 --> 00:49:44,454
He's quite ill and really wants to see me settled down before he dies.

540
00:49:45,538 --> 00:49:47,748
Oh, is he really ill?

541
00:49:50,110 --> 00:49:52,003
One of my relatives is getting married today.

542
00:49:52,003 --> 00:50:00,086
And today is the last day that grandfather gets to leave the hospital.

543
00:50:02,146 --> 00:50:06,243
Oh, okay, fine!

544
00:50:07,952 --> 00:50:12,398
I don't want to participate in your lie, but I'll agree to this for now.

545
00:50:12,398 --> 00:50:15,402
But in exchange, if you try to pull anything,

546
00:50:15,402 --> 00:50:17,695
I really won't stand for it.

547
00:50:18,597 --> 00:50:21,925
All right. Okay. Since we're engaged, we should introduce ourselves.

548
00:50:21,925 --> 00:50:24,819
I'm Kang Hyeon Min. And you are?

549
00:50:24,819 --> 00:50:27,363
I'm Eun Ha Won.

550
00:50:34,529 --> 00:50:36,673
Wow, you sure are strange.

551
00:50:36,673 --> 00:50:39,451
How is it that you're looking elsewhere when you're right next to me?

552
00:50:40,227 --> 00:50:41,870
What's wrong with you?

553
00:50:42,704 --> 00:50:44,239
Don't act like we are close.

554
00:50:44,247 --> 00:50:49,127
Hey, we're engaged, you know. So we should try to act the part.

555
00:50:49,127 --> 00:50:50,979
Forget it!

556
00:50:54,591 --> 00:50:56,810
You'll be my fiancée for three hours tonight.

557
00:50:56,810 --> 00:50:59,737
A chance like this won't come again, so let's have fun.

558
00:51:01,181 --> 00:51:04,975
All of this will be over at midnight on the dot!

559
00:51:09,800 --> 00:51:14,700
This is the location of Haneul Group's Chairman's fifth wedding!

560
00:51:14,700 --> 00:51:18,832
They say Korean royalty will be divided into two categories tonight:

561
00:51:18,832 --> 00:51:22,577
those who were invited to this wedding, and those who were not.

562
00:51:22,577 --> 00:51:25,296
However, the biggest question tonight is

563
00:51:25,296 --> 00:51:31,294
will the Kang cousins, who've never been seen together in one place, all show up?

564
00:51:40,103 --> 00:51:42,480
- Who the hell is that?
- Who is that?

565
00:51:42,480 --> 00:51:43,881
- Hey!
- Who the hell is that?

566
00:51:43,881 --> 00:51:45,775
Lady Killer Kang Hyeon Min has made his entrance!

567
00:51:45,775 --> 00:51:48,728
What the— What girl did he bring?

568
00:52:03,034 --> 00:52:05,661
Kang Seo Woo, who is the youngest cousin and a huge star, arrived.

569
00:52:05,661 --> 00:52:08,639
He's definitely the most handsome!

570
00:52:11,585 --> 00:52:16,706
Now, if the rebellious Kang Ji Woon shows up,

571
00:52:16,706 --> 00:52:19,000
then all three cousins will have shown up.

572
00:52:19,000 --> 00:52:22,311
Will Kang Ji Woon come to the wedding?

573
00:52:47,704 --> 00:52:49,823
What's all this?

574
00:52:49,900 --> 00:52:54,000
You have to transform into my fiancee now. Let' play!

575
00:53:10,285 --> 00:53:11,644
What?

576
00:53:12,537 --> 00:53:15,606
- Are you with someone?
- Yeah.

577
00:53:16,333 --> 00:53:17,784
- Who?
- You don't know her.

578
00:53:19,803 --> 00:53:22,163
What kind of girl is she?

579
00:53:24,908 --> 00:53:27,836
Don't you get tired of obsessing over me?

580
00:53:28,511 --> 00:53:33,358
This has nothing to do with you, so mind your own business.

581
00:54:01,519 --> 00:54:05,532
He wants me to wear this? What a total pervert!

582
00:54:06,116 --> 00:54:10,787
Should I just quit now and tell him to find someone else?

583
00:54:11,288 --> 00:54:16,459
No, I can't do that. His grandfather is waiting.

584
00:55:27,931 --> 00:55:29,574
All done.

585
00:55:49,727 --> 00:55:53,264
What the hell is this? This isn't a children's choir!

586
00:55:53,264 --> 00:55:56,993
I ate so many raw eggs to be chosen for this!

587
00:55:56,993 --> 00:56:02,231
I'm the prettiest one here. It's okay. Let's do this!

588
00:56:20,575 --> 00:56:25,180
I'm halfway there now. Halfway there.

589
00:56:26,890 --> 00:56:30,594
- We're ready now, Chairman.
- Okay.

590
00:56:32,304 --> 00:56:35,265
It's showtime. Let's go.

591
00:57:58,514 --> 00:58:01,342
- What's going on?
- What is he doing?

592
00:58:02,727 --> 00:58:06,339
- What are we doing right now?
- The wedding march.

593
00:58:07,082 --> 00:58:10,860
- We're getting married.
- What?

594
00:58:13,864 --> 00:58:16,457
- Hey, are you crazy?
- No.

595
00:58:16,975 --> 00:58:18,894
Hey, this is different from what you told me!

596
00:58:18,894 --> 00:58:21,096
It's only a tiny bit different. A tiny bit.

597
00:58:21,096 --> 00:58:23,473
- We can't do this.
- It's fine!

598
00:58:23,473 --> 00:58:27,752
- What are you trying to pull here?
- People are waiting. Come on.

599
00:58:27,752 --> 00:58:30,205
No, this isn't right!

600
00:58:33,675 --> 00:58:34,951
Let's go.

601
00:58:34,968 --> 00:58:37,529
What are you doing? Put me down, now!

602
00:58:37,529 --> 00:58:39,255
Shush! Be quiet.

603
00:58:44,902 --> 00:58:46,721
- Oh my.
- What's going on?

604
00:59:00,568 --> 00:59:06,458
My lovely grandfather, I give you my fiancee as your wedding present.

605
00:59:07,100 --> 00:59:10,000
Why, you... You!

606
00:59:10,654 --> 00:59:12,339
- Fiancee?
- Oh my!

607
00:59:12,339 --> 00:59:15,183
Where are you from, young lady?

608
00:59:15,183 --> 00:59:16,859
What?

609
00:59:16,859 --> 00:59:19,729
If you're someone that our Hyeon Min would bring here—

610
00:59:19,729 --> 00:59:22,098
Um, I'm a senior at Jeongsan Girls' High.

611
00:59:28,480 --> 00:59:34,794
Hey, say hello. This is my grandfather's fifth wife.

612
00:59:35,662 --> 00:59:38,748
You. How dare you speak so rudely!

613
00:59:38,748 --> 00:59:43,753
I'm sorry! It wasn't my intention to ruin your special day!

614
00:59:43,753 --> 00:59:48,591
- Hey, what are you doing?
- That's what I'd like to ask you!

615
00:59:48,591 --> 00:59:52,403
You're rebelling toward your grandfather here, of all places? You're not a child!

616
00:59:52,403 --> 00:59:55,273
What are you doing? Hurry up and apologize!

617
00:59:55,273 --> 00:59:57,191
