- I don't want to.

619
01:00:09,955 --> 01:00:11,614
I'm so sorry.

620
01:00:29,391 --> 01:00:31,476
Time out. I'm leaving.

621
01:00:31,476 --> 01:00:34,329
Hey, no round two?

622
01:00:34,329 --> 01:00:35,681
No.

623
01:00:36,231 --> 01:00:39,576
What, she's really your fiancee?

624
01:00:40,552 --> 01:00:45,724
Of course! Say hello. You know him, right? He's the singer, Kang Seo Woo.

625
01:00:46,308 --> 01:00:49,311
We're cousins. It's nice to meet you.

626
01:00:52,272 --> 01:00:54,341
The time right now is...

627
01:00:54,341 --> 01:00:56,234
Oh... yes.

628
01:00:57,110 --> 01:01:01,505
Aren't you being too much right now, to Hye Ji?

629
01:01:05,577 --> 01:01:08,779
It's not like I have any relationship with Park Hye Ji.

630
01:01:09,831 --> 01:01:14,343
How about you stop overreacting in front of my girl?

631
01:01:27,490 --> 01:01:30,501
So, you're Hyeon Min's fiancee?

632
01:01:31,369 --> 01:01:33,163
Um, yeah.

633
01:01:33,230 --> 01:01:36,783
I'm Park Hye Ji. I've been friends with Hyeon Min since we were young.

634
01:01:37,459 --> 01:01:41,196
- Nice to meet you.
- Yeah.

635
01:01:44,741 --> 01:01:48,978
"Nice to meet you?" Have you no pride?

636
01:01:49,663 --> 01:01:53,032
Ji Woon. What are you doing?

637
01:01:55,627 --> 01:01:58,171
Did you come all the way here because of money?

638
01:01:59,481 --> 01:02:02,533
Do you really need money that badly?

639
01:02:31,310 --> 01:02:34,300
♫  While I keep looking only at you ♫

